                        <support>1 papyrus ; 9.3 x 20.9 cm</support>
                        <condition>
                           <ab type="conservation">A light-brown papyrus with dark stain; cut off straight at the left-hand side and at the top. At the top there is a margin left of 1.5 cm., at the left one of 1 cm. and at the bottom one of 5 cm. The lines on the right run up to the very edge. There is a kollesis ca. 2 cm. from the edge at the right. Two vertical folds are still visible. The papyrus has been used before and there are still traces of letters discernible, especially in the lefty-hand margin, which do not belong to the present text.</ab>
                        </condition>
